219
00:14:42,635 --> 00:14:43,595
Dracarys.

220
00:14:43,635 --> 00:14:45,075
Drogon lança fogo nele,

221
00:14:45,115 --> 00:14:46,795
mas não vemos
nosso amigo queimar.

222
00:14:46,835 --> 00:14:49,155
